de.mrapp.android.adapter.datastructure.item

Class UnmodifiableItemList<DataType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mrapp.android.adapter.datastructure.AbstractUnmodifiableList<DataType,Item<DataType>>
      • de.mrapp.android.adapter.datastructure.item.UnmodifiableItemList<DataType>
  • Type Parameters:
    DataType - The type of the underlying data of the list's items
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Unmodifiable, java.lang.Iterable<DataType>, java.util.Collection<DataType>, java.util.List<DataType>

    public class UnmodifiableItemList<DataType>
extends AbstractUnmodifiableList<DataType,Item<DataType>>
    An implementation of the type List, which throws exceptions of the type UnsupportedOperationException when attempted to be modified. Such a list encapsulates an other list, which contains items of the type Item.
    Since:
    0.1.0
